#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an5.210"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.210:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.210:0.2"
msgid "21. Kimilavagga "
msgstr "21. With Kimbila "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.210:0.3"
msgid "210. Muṭṭhassatisutta "
msgstr "210. Unmindful "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an5.210:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, ādīnavā muṭṭhassatissa asampajānassa niddaṃ okkamayato. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five drawbacks of falling asleep unmindful and unaware. "

msgctxt "an5.210:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.210:1.3"
msgid "Dukkhaṃ supati, dukkhaṃ paṭibujjhati, pāpakaṃ supinaṃ passati, devatā na rakkhanti, asuci muccati. "
msgstr "You sleep badly and wake miserably. You have bad dreams. The deities don’t protect you. And you emit semen. "

msgctxt "an5.210:1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ādīnavā muṭṭhassatissa asampajānassa niddaṃ okkamayato. "
msgstr "These are the five drawbacks of falling asleep unmindful and unaware. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an5.210:2.1"
msgid "Pañcime, bhikkhave, ānisaṃsā upaṭṭhitassatissa sampajānassa niddaṃ okkamayato. "
msgstr "There are these five benefits of falling asleep mindful and aware. "

msgctxt "an5.210:2.2"
msgid "Katame pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.210:2.3"
msgid "Sukhaṃ supati, sukhaṃ paṭibujjhati, na pāpakaṃ supinaṃ passati, devatā rakkhanti, asuci na muccati. "
msgstr "You sleep well and wake happily. You don’t have bad dreams. The deities protect you. And you don’t emit semen. "

msgctxt "an5.210:2.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ānisaṃsā upaṭṭhitassatissa sampajānassa niddaṃ okkamayato”ti. "
msgstr "These are the five benefits of falling asleep mindful and aware.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.210:2.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.210:2.6"
msgid "Kimilavaggo paṭhamo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an5.210:3.1"
msgid "Kimilo dhammassavanaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.210:3.2"
msgid "ājānīyo balaṃ khilaṃ; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.210:3.3"
msgid "Vinibandhaṃ yāgu kaṭṭhaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.210:3.4"
msgid "gītaṃ muṭṭhassatinā cāti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
